Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是2D4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將進入東京租界管轄空域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 飛行目的確認為廣告宣傳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無變更
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滯空時間也按照申報 預定為14小時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認 允許上空飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝應對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾與ZERO攜手震驚布里塔尼亞的黑色騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只剩下我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 還沒到絕望的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這次飛燕四號作戰成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:00:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本 萬歲！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本 萬歲！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 真纏人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次你別想再逃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.83,0:01:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 之前那事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.23,0:01:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 下次說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副會長 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始比體力 你就輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是誇張了點 不過是體育補習
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就乖乖來上課
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我學分應該夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是有色氣體罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 副會長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這學生會長怎麼當的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別殺我啊 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利瓦爾 幾時…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利瓦爾 這借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯又犯了？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,0)}魔神 覺醒 之 日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 放學後還不給人自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這還不都怪哥哥成天逃課嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懶得去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰問品 會長給的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO掀起的謀反事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色叛亂過後將近一年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11區也已完全平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件當初有過各種傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兄弟倆也想過回布里塔尼亞本國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志願調查表交了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維蕾塔老師都生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算上大學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當學生也當膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又不想聽人使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就算出了社會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:05:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上層也都被大企業或貴族佔據了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是走進成型的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納入大人們的金字塔而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是對11區人的歧視 是區別
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11區人被ZERO這詐騙犯所操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖恢復日本人之名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好戰的危險人種
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此必須被我們布里塔尼亞人管理教育
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11區輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒實力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若老實聽話 也不至於被貶為強制教育區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO…真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論做什麼 都改變不了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡快 卡拉雷斯總督
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中華聯邦的諸位…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機情局的作戰計劃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 在巴別塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏挑這個日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下到底在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今雖不認為黑色騎士團殘黨還能有何作為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個ZERO已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別偷懶 11區的人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標已到達 和預想一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由B3進入第5大門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次會出現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出現就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都冒險放他去租界外沿部了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你只要送我來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還是非法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不止警告處分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕什麼警察
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼 哥哥不是為了錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用問 是為了和更強的人對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不過是無聊的消遣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 今天萬眾矚目的兄弟對決
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倖存的會是哥哥 還是弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的比賽已連續進行了10輪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs24}哥哥 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不好嗎 一目瞭然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 開懷享樂的是我們布里塔尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣力受人恥笑的是11區人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算假裝無視 結果也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11區輸了兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木首相和ZERO都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有實力還謀什麼反…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是11區人 而您是布里塔尼亞的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更不用這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭炫耀身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒實力的人必須忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使錯在對方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把你們的價值觀強加於我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的「獵兔」收穫頗豐 真是可喜可賀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是商品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是商品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗者沒有人權
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安定因素 發生糾紛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怪就怪自己投錯胎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下也這麼說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱肉強食 這就是世界的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 是黑社會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為自己就算掠食者了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生 這是大人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 大人的世界和學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰才是掠食者 用這個弄個明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國際象棋？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生真是不諳世事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒未必
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗王者先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這個世界是赫赫有名的棋手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知道還來挑戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是ZERO還在 誰怕你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別提那個叛徒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO才不是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有什麼內情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內情？大決戰中指揮官跑了還要什麼內情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.20,0:09:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.93,0:09:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 ZERO已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗王者居然輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還輕而易舉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來弱肉的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事要是傳出去 我可就丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒興趣四處炫耀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 學生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說你出千的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出千？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下棋怎麼出千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 偽造點證據吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骯髒的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相可不值錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖襲擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用飛船 垂死掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機密情報局 瓦爾哈拉七號行動開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨11區
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好隆重的接待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過聽說ZERO已經死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是要讓中華聯邦的各位理解我們布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣比較明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地直截了當嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交出您腰上的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治安可以保證 這種老古董…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻 太無禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是要讓各位理解我們中華聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣比較明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 目標跟丟了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我們正準備突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊巴別塔的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎持有數架Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始同時 周邊已清理完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 進入第7階段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 卡拉雷斯總督…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方管理層無視就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是奉皇帝陛下之命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11區的走樓梯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超重啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色騎士團的殘黨怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布里塔尼亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 都怪我沒抓好他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別介意 卜部他們正在找
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非 是對我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 接下來怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 絕對能逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯真是 連羅洛都拖下水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說吧 你是擔心魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少來這套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅…羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不通 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一定要救他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少應該能救出唯一的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點力量我應該也有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子干的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 連11區人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還執著於ZERO那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要殺我嗎 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算逃也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來接你了 魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的敵人是布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我訂過契約吧 我們是共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約？共犯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我瞭解 真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的…我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯…魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 人還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修·蘭佩洛奇同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務？說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在監視你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6點59分起床
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7點12分和弟弟一起邊看新聞邊吃早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視聽內容無思想性偏向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8點45分上學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未出席班會和第一堂課 在屋頂看書
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二堂物理課…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今天的…我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是誘餌的飼養日記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誘餌？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說陷阱也行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了引出那個魔女 C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒興趣跟誘餌說太多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 該處分掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就沒有目擊者了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處分？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…要死？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明不白的 這麼輕易就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃離這裡的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝過世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音 是剛才的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量你已經有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被封鎖在忘卻之籠中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 解除封印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如荊棘般刺入我生活的焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是虛偽的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不求你原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們 是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的回答嗎 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處分我之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女的還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 明明射穿了心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若無力是罪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那力量就是正義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇就是罪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友誼就算是正義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼罪惡正義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誘餌只有死亡一途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼也給你們一條路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修·V·布里塔尼亞下令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜你們 一死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天起 我心中就無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不自然的虛偽生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯離的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶被篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家畜般的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實一直在追求我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 錯的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界將會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠改變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等候多時了 ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請下令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我就是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死ZERO的 將是我
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不饒恕 不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的記憶是僅屬於我的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.49,0:23:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是保持自我的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而有人卻將其踐踏 視為馴養家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者作為餌食 蔑視至極
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,償還的時刻到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.49,0:23:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO回歸這一事實的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要讓布里塔尼亞回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.40,0:24:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛偽的統治 已不再需要


